<font color="#FF0000">FOR MY FATHER</font><br>
<tt>Tue Dec  3  0:48:17 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
My father told me this poem when I would ask him about Vietnam...                                                                   For those who fought for it<br>
                 Life has a Special Flavor                                   That the protected Will                                     Never know                                                               UK                                                          SVN                           He is lookin for his buddies in the 4 th Combined Action Platoon  third squad  third platoon USMC 67-68 Mike Inog, Comstock, Thor, Willy form Philly, Sam Guess, and Scott.    It has been a long time for him, and he has alvays told me that over there you did not really know their real names, you just got on the helo and left...                   
